### SECURITY FIX PATTERNS ###
| Vulnerability | Fix Pattern |
|--------------|-------------|
| SQL Injection | Use parameterized queries: `cursor.execute("SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ?", (user_id,))` |
| Command Injection | Use subprocess with list args: `subprocess.run(['cmd', arg], shell=False)` |
| Hardcoded Credentials | Use environment variables: `os.getenv('SECRET_KEY')` |
| Insecure Random | Use secrets module: `secrets.token_hex(16)` |
